reviewText: Everybody needs to hear this.  Everybody!

Dispenza is a light vessel. The proof is in the pudding. If you want to play on a larger scale this is the recipe on how to do it. His meditation reconditioning the body to a mind is perfect complimentary to this, watch empower and then do. Life changes.
Braden and Dispenza together bring together macrocosmic and microcosmic views of our lives that serve to inform and inspire.
